WEBVTT

00:05.948 --> 00:07.183
There was a flu epidemic.

00:07.284 --> 00:08.718
In the early '90s.

00:08.818 --> 00:10.687
Seven percent of the population
was wiped out.

00:10.688 --> 00:12.475
That's, like,
half a billion people.

00:12.476 --> 00:13.154
LAMBERT: We know that your world

00:13.155 --> 00:15.858
had no part in the pandemic
that decimated our cities.

00:15.958 --> 00:18.428
- Okay, Claude...
- Was the topic off-limits, Fancher?

00:18.528 --> 00:19.962
I wonder if there'll ever
come a reckoning,

00:20.062 --> 00:21.764
for what they did to us.

00:21.864 --> 00:24.200
You know anything about this
group Pope is working with?

00:24.301 --> 00:26.836
- Lambert's part of it, too.
- They're fanatics.

00:26.936 --> 00:28.505
ALICE: It's a black operation.
They're called Indigo.

00:28.605 --> 00:31.441
- A network of some kind?
- ALICE: School.

00:33.443 --> 00:36.479
And are placed here,
as sleeper agents.

00:36.579 --> 00:39.081
After all the work
that they did to place you here,

00:39.181 --> 00:40.717
would you really risk
this mission

00:40.817 --> 00:42.752
when we're so close
to the big day?

00:42.852 --> 00:44.321
These documents were stolen
from my department?

00:44.421 --> 00:46.155
Whoever is getting information
from your floor,

00:46.255 --> 00:48.157
they're getting it from you.

00:48.257 --> 00:49.392
ALDRICH: It's Quayle.

00:49.492 --> 00:51.127
He's the perfect spy.

00:51.227 --> 00:53.296
[Baby crying in distance]

00:57.600 --> 00:59.669
How was your day, birthday boy?

