26:19.354 --> 26:22.557
[Woman speaking German
over P.A.]

26:46.481 --> 26:48.016
POPE: Once you've made it
to their side,

26:48.116 --> 26:49.918
walk across the bridge,

26:50.018 --> 26:54.489
follow the Spree River west
to the safe house.

26:57.993 --> 27:00.061
There, you will meet
your contact.

27:02.097 --> 27:04.532
The man who will be
your sole lifeline

27:04.632 --> 27:06.734
during the time you're there.

27:06.834 --> 27:09.037
His name is Claude Lambert.

27:09.137 --> 27:12.974
Bit of a cad,
but you can trust him.

27:13.074 --> 27:14.809
How was your journey?

27:14.910 --> 27:17.312
Uh, when am I being inserted?

27:17.412 --> 27:19.881
My dear.

27:19.981 --> 27:22.383
Let us be clear about something.

27:22.483 --> 27:26.888
Your friends and I,
we have a special arrangement.

27:26.988 --> 27:29.724
But to you,
I'm just a messenger.

27:29.824 --> 27:33.128
Understood?

27:33.228 --> 27:35.796
Good.

27:35.897 --> 27:37.698
How do I reach you?

27:37.798 --> 27:38.900
If I need you.

27:39.000 --> 27:41.302
Well, we don't need people.

27:41.402 --> 27:43.471
We want them.

27:43.571 --> 27:44.772
Oh.

27:44.872 --> 27:47.442
Uh...

27:47.542 --> 27:49.677
Here we are.

27:49.777 --> 27:51.346
Hold onto this.

27:51.446 --> 27:55.650
