32:05.266 --> 32:06.434
- to see you.
- Thank you.

32:06.534 --> 32:08.436
- Hey.
- Hi. Love your necklace.

32:08.536 --> 32:09.270
Thank you.

32:09.370 --> 32:10.438
It's from Croatia.

32:10.538 --> 32:11.772
Hello, mate.

32:11.872 --> 32:13.007
