32:46.674 --> 32:48.142
- Take one little peek.
- Okay, go.

32:48.243 --> 32:50.845
Just a little.

32:50.945 --> 32:52.913
How many is that?

33:06.427 --> 33:08.095
QUAYLE:
So, what are we drinking to?

33:08.195 --> 33:12.267
