35:33.107 --> 35:34.509
Huh.

35:34.609 --> 35:36.276
Well, that'll have to change.

35:36.377 --> 35:39.246
Uh, if you want your replacement
to be authentic, that is.

35:39.346 --> 35:41.849
One cannot have
their cherry popped twice.

35:44.018 --> 35:45.620
