36:12.079 --> 36:15.249
[Rock music playing]

36:15.349 --> 36:17.051
[Pool balls break]

36:33.300 --> 36:35.570
Whiskey.

36:38.072 --> 36:39.406
[Speaks German]

36:44.645 --> 36:47.648
[Speaking German]

36:48.883 --> 36:50.618
Danke.

37:03.631 --> 37:06.033
[Grunting rhythmically]

37:19.346 --> 37:21.215
I want to be on top.

37:21.315 --> 37:22.550
Okay.

37:31.526 --> 37:35.162
[Glass clinking]

37:35.262 --> 37:36.631
