41:15.215 --> 41:17.351
I want you out.

41:17.451 --> 41:20.320
[Door opens onscreen]

41:20.420 --> 41:22.689
[Door shuts onscreen]

41:22.790 --> 41:25.159
[Thunder rumbling]

41:28.428 --> 41:30.430
