41:34.802 --> 41:35.870
Patch it up quickly,

41:35.970 --> 41:37.671
before it gets out of hand.

41:37.772 --> 41:41.275
The girl was about to marry
a deputy director.

41:41.375 --> 41:43.443
I don't suppose
you're naive enough to assume

41:43.543 --> 41:46.513
