your operation if she doesn't.

41:46.613 --> 41:49.016
You have enough operating cash.

41:49.116 --> 41:51.651
Hire a team,
and you get to work.

41:51.752 --> 41:53.153
Now.

42:00.027 --> 42:02.462
[Clacking, rustling]

42:23.383 --> 42:25.419
