No. No, I'm sorry.

45:13.053 --> 45:15.155
I'm so sorry.

45:15.255 --> 45:19.059
- ♪ It was easy for me.
- [Sniffles]

45:19.159 --> 45:21.628
♪ To cheat and lie

45:21.728 --> 45:23.730
♪ 'Cause I thought
you'd never say good-bye ♪

45:23.830 --> 45:25.699
I love you so much.

45:25.799 --> 45:28.768
<i>♪</i>

45:28.868 --> 45:30.570
♪ Girl

45:30.670 --> 45:34.208
- [crying]
- ♪ But now that you're gone

45:34.308 --> 45:37.644
♪ And I'm all alone

45:37.744 --> 45:38.778
♪ My nights.

45:38.878 --> 45:39.879
AVA: Roland, please,

45:39.980 --> 45:41.415
skip the gory part.

45:41.515 --> 45:45.119
ROLAND: She broke both of her legs.

45:45.219 --> 45:47.787
Couldn't walk for six months.

45:47.887 --> 45:49.856
My little girl was miserable.

45:49.956 --> 45:51.825
- He loves telling this story.
- [Chuckles]

45:51.925 --> 45:56.330
I do. I do.
Because I am so proud...

45:56.430 --> 45:59.699
<i>♪</i>

45:59.799 --> 46:02.002
could have ever imagined.

46:02.102 --> 46:04.304
Thanks, Daddy.

46:05.272 --> 46:08.308
♪ Living without you

46:08.408 --> 46:13.413
♪ My days are dark as night

46:14.914 --> 46:16.750
♪ It's hard.

46:16.850 --> 46:18.618
Is he all right?

46:18.718 --> 46:20.320
Yeah.

46:20.420 --> 46:22.689
I don't think he likes
remembering his own mortality.

46:22.789 --> 46:25.225
[chuckles]
Well, who does?

46:25.325 --> 46:29.996
- ♪ Swear I'll make things right ♪
- Good night.

46:30.097 --> 46:32.066
- ♪ I'll make it easy ♪
- Thank you.

46:32.166 --> 46:34.101
[Indistinct conversations
in other room]

46:34.201 --> 46:36.436
- CLARE: Mariel.
- Thank you for having us.

46:36.536 --> 46:37.937
Take care.

46:38.038 --> 46:39.639
Would you like
to keep me company while I...

46:39.739 --> 46:41.375
I think we should let
the happy couple get

46:41.475 --> 46:43.643
- a good night's rest tonight, hmm?
- Okay.

46:43.743 --> 46:47.947
I suppose I could forgo this
for one night.

46:48.048 --> 46:49.583
Yes, you really should.

46:49.683 --> 46:53.153
Give this back to Peter
and tell him thanks anyway

46:53.253 --> 46:55.655
and happy birthday.

46:55.755 --> 46:57.291
Good night, sweetheart.

46:57.391 --> 46:58.758
CLARE: Good night.

46:58.858 --> 47:01.628
Love you.

47:01.728 --> 47:04.131
[Crickets chirping]

47:10.404 --> 47:13.039
[Car starts in distance]

47:38.865 --> 47:41.301
[Drawer shuts]

47:42.302 --> 47:45.004
[Crickets chirping]

47:45.105 --> 47:47.507
[Water running]

47:47.607 --> 47:49.343
[Water stops]

47:56.650 --> 48:00.254
I think Mariel and Friedrich
are fighting.

48:00.354 --> 48:03.623
Barely said a word to her
all night.

48:07.093 --> 48:08.862
That was some toast you gave.

48:08.962 --> 48:10.797
Yeah, I was feeling nostalgic.

48:10.897 --> 48:13.367
I could see that.

48:14.534 --> 48:17.771
You ever like to look back,
Clare?

48:18.905 --> 48:20.740
You like to...

48:20.840 --> 48:22.709
reflect on your life?

48:22.809 --> 48:24.010
Your family?

48:24.110 --> 48:25.945
You're drunk.

48:26.045 --> 48:27.147
But you're...

48:27.247 --> 48:29.115
always very composed.

48:29.216 --> 48:30.384
Aren't you?

48:30.484 --> 48:32.118
[Sighs]

48:32.219 --> 48:34.188
I go to all this trouble,

48:34.288 --> 48:36.290
slave away to throw you
the perfect night...

48:36.390 --> 48:38.792
Perfect night in a perfect life.

48:42.296 --> 48:45.232
You know everything about her,
don't you?

48:46.266 --> 48:50.003
You know every little detail.

48:50.103 --> 48:53.039
Or has it been you,

48:53.139 --> 48:55.775
just playing me this whole time?

48:55.875 --> 48:57.811
[Scoffs]

48:58.878 --> 49:00.780
Tell me...

49:00.880 --> 49:02.816
Clare.

49:03.950 --> 49:06.653
Where did she end

49:06.753 --> 49:09.689
and you begin?

49:09.789 --> 49:11.891
Hmm?

49:11.991 --> 49:14.761
Did I ever even fuck
my real wife?

49:14.861 --> 49:16.095
You want to fuck me?

49:16.196 --> 49:18.232
I said "my wife"!

49:18.332 --> 49:20.734
[Yelps, grunts]

49:20.834 --> 49:23.503
[Baby crying in distance]

49:29.343 --> 49:31.177
This your way out, Clare?

49:31.278 --> 49:33.046
Hmm? You ever get caught,

49:33.146 --> 49:34.514
one little swallow,
it all goes away?

49:34.614 --> 49:37.016
- Fuck you!
- Take it, you fucking spy!

49:37.116 --> 49:39.219
I'm giving you a way out.
Take it!

49:39.319 --> 49:41.655
[Crying continues in distance]

49:43.390 --> 49:46.159
It won't do anything, Peter.

49:46.260 --> 49:48.595
I let it go bad.

49:49.729 --> 49:52.499
It expired.

49:54.434 --> 49:56.336
Don't you understand?

49:56.436 --> 49:58.372
[sniffles]
All my life,

49:58.472 --> 50:01.841
I never had anything of my own.

50:03.009 --> 50:05.545
But things are different now.

50:07.847 --> 50:09.516
How?

50:09.616 --> 50:11.685
[Crying continues in distance]

50:15.289 --> 50:17.691
[Fussing]

50:22.762 --> 50:25.164
[Fussing stops]

50:25.265 --> 50:27.834
NURSE: Just give her a minute.

50:27.934 --> 50:30.404
[Fussing softly]

50:32.205 --> 50:34.173
[Chuckles softly]

50:34.274 --> 50:36.209
How'd she know how to...

50:36.310 --> 50:39.713
'Cause, dear, she's yours.

50:42.282 --> 50:44.684
What will you call her?

50:44.784 --> 50:46.386
For the register.

50:50.824 --> 50:52.892
Spencer.

50:57.431 --> 51:00.467
Call her Spencer.

